  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "when using `yalc` to compile the master branch and add to a project from the [contributing guide](https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#yarn-pack), I receive when running the `npx hardhat accounts` command:\r\n\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ npx hardhat accounts\r\n'hardhat' is not recognized as an internal or external command,\r\noperable program or batch file\r\n```\r\n\r\nPrior to getting this error, I installed the hardhat package with:\r\n\r\n1. Go to `packages/hardhat-core` and run `yalc publish`\r\n2. Go to some hardhat project and run `yalc add hardhat`",
